    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cucumber rounds</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 1/4<strong> </strong>of your <strong>wholegrain mustard </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
