    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a small bowl with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Put your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in the oven for 5 min or until hot and crusty, then slice in half</p>",
