    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is golden, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[250ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the liquid has reduced to a thick gravy-like consistency – this is your <strong>Fable mushroom 'brisket'</strong></p>",
